model.util

Class Dataset

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.util.Dataset

  • public class Dataset
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to retrieve the dataset information from Enefficient's database hosted on MLab powered by the MongoDB framework. The Dataset class separates all of its appliance data by type of appliance.
    Author:
    Sagar Thomas

    • Method Detail

      • init

        public static boolean init()
        This method initializes the local database by retrieving the data stored in MongoDB. The local data is available until the end of the REST API call so every new REST API call must call this method before using it.
        Returns:
        true if initialization is successful and false otherwise.
